TITLE: Arkansas Sen. Tom Cotton not running for president in 2024
SUMMARY: Republican Sen. Tom Cotton of Arkansas, a rising star in the GOP, has decided against seeking the presidency in the 2024 election cycle

TITLE: Lions hand Aaron Rodgers, Packers fifth straight loss
SUMMARY: The Detroit Lions stunned Aaron Rodgers and the Green Bay Packers on Sunday, winning 15-6. Rodgers and the offense struggled in big spots.

TITLE: Democrats call in the cavalry trying to save blue seat in key Senate battleground
SUMMARY: Sen. Amy Klobuchar of Minnesota joined her Democratic colleague Sen. Maggie Hassan in New Hampshire two days before Election Day to urge supporters "to turn out the vote."

TITLE: Never-Trump columnist gets pummeled for saying 'other than murder, violent crime is not up'
SUMMARY: The Bulwark columnist Mona Charen’s tweet claiming that violent crime “other than murder” did not go up nationally went viral on Twitter over the weekend.

TITLE: Cameron Dicker's clutch kicks lift Chargers to three-point win
SUMMARY: Los Angeles Chargers kicker Cameron Dicker nailed two late field goals to help the team narrowly beat the Atlanta Falcons, 20-17, on Sunday.

TITLE: Bengals' Joe Mixon carries offense with five touchdowns, blows out Panthers at home
SUMMARY: Cincinnati Bengals running back Joe Mixon beat up the Carolina Panthers' defense, scoring five touchdowns to help pick up a 42-21 win on Sunday.

TITLE: New York governor: Lee Zeldin supporter attacked at rally for Gov. Kathy Hochul, video shows
SUMMARY: A female supporter of GOP gubernatorial candidate Lee Zeldin says she was attacked and assaulted at a rally for Democratic Gov. Kathy Hochul in New York City on Saturday.

TITLE: Ex-MLB star Lenny Dykstra pins Phillies' World Series struggles on Jill Biden's appearance
SUMMARY: Jill Biden took in the Philadelphia Phillies' Game 4 loss to the Houston Astros, and Lenny Dykstra said her appearance changed everything.

TITLE: Austin police release bodycam footage of shootout with armed suspect hiding on restaurant's patio
SUMMARY: Body camera footage released by the Austin Police Department shows officers exchanging gunfire with a suspect who was displaying a gun in a "threatening manner."

TITLE: GOP could win key Florida county for the first time in two decades
SUMMARY: Republicans are threatening to win Florida's typicall blue Miami-Dade County, which has not voted for a Republican candidate for governor since Jeb Bush two decades ago.
